ygData.msgSnippet: In a message dated 7/10/99 5:12:58 AM Central Daylight Time, EQ_SMITHS@onelist.com writes:
ygData.messageBody:
In a message dated 7/10/99 5:12:58 AM Central Daylight Time,
EQ_SMITHS@onelist.com writes:

<< If you even bother selling for these prices you are part of the problem. I
am not meaning this as an attack at you, but rather as an observation. As I
stated I don't care that much as I simply won't sell at these prices I would
rather hunt somwhere and get exp and loot than waste my time making banded
armor. >>

I dot make it, it is left over inventory that I have in the bank that I have
been trying to get rid of for weeks. I made some for the sole purpose of
practice and now I cant dump it. I would not normally sell for that low. If
you every hear my sales pitch you will hear me say that I am having a
"clearance sale." When I dump these items, my prices will likely go back up.

Hawkwin of Hawkwin's Roaming Emporium
